  "original_title": "\u0dc3\u0dde\u0d9b\u0dca\u200d\u0dba \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dbd\u0db0\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dd3\u0d9c\u0dda \u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc3\u0dca \u0db4\u0ddc\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd \u0d9a\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dc4\u0dbd\u0dcf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "The health officer's nostrils were broken",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Kalutara South Police said that investigations are being conducted to find a person who is said to have hit the health officer with a helmet causing his nose to burst following an incident where a civil defense force officer collided with a car driven by a Kalutara health officer today (01).",
        "The victim was identified as Gamage Aruna Kumara Perera, 40, a resident of Nagahawatta, Maha Gonaduwa, Morontuduwa.",
        "The victim was on duty as an Entomologist at the Kalutara District Secretariat.",
        "The police say that a person passing by intervened in the conversation that took place at that moment, and then he hit the health officer in the face with the helmet he was holding.",
        "According to hospital sources, the health officer who was attacked has been admitted to Kalutara General Hospital, and whether the main bone of his nose has been damaged, he has been admitted to the intensive care unit and tests are being conducted.",
        "Police are conducting investigations to find the person who escaped the attack.",
        "Investigations are being carried out under the direction of Kalutara HQI Sunil Shantha under the direction of OIC of the Complaints Division, Chief Inspector Silva."
      ],
